						<summary>

						

						<p>This is a badly damaged Telugu inscription dated merely in the (cyclic) year Khara, Chaitra, ba. 10. It seems to record the grant of a village near Tēnēpalle to a certain••••• Gāvuṇḍa by an agent of <hi rend="bold">Timmarāja</hi> the son of <hi rend="bold">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara-Tirumalarāja.</hi></p>						

